LocateU is an APP that keeps you in touch with your family and friends at all times. Find a friend through mobile phone number, and after obtaining his/her consent, and you can view his/her real-time location information so as to protect the safety of you and your family, even if they are thousands of miles away.
LocateU is the bond between family members:
No matter where you are, you can get real-time location information of your family;
You can know where your family has been by viewing their tracking history;
In case of danger, you can ask your family for help with just one click to protect the safety of family members; 
Track mobile phone after it is stolen or lost
Share your location with family members;
Even when you're busy, it is easy to get in touch with your family; 
In need of help, your family can get the message at the first time; 
Optional permission request:
Location services, to inform your family of your current location;
Contacts, to find other users to add as friends;
Storage, to store your tracking history;
Note: Location information can only be shared with friends after they agree. We are very concerned about the privacy of you and your family; therefore, please share location information with people you trust.
In addition, LocateU collects location information only for real-time location sharing between friends and for emergency help, while the app is in use or after it is closed.
For our privacy policy and terms of use, please click:
https://api.locate-u.com/html/privacy.html
https://api.locate-u.com/html/service.html
You can also go to the APP customer service page for feedback and suggestions.

Приложение GoTrans предоставляет информацию о расписании движения автобусов и троллейбусов города Гомеля

GoTrans это:
- быстрый доступ к расписанию автобусов и троллейбусов;
- поиск остановок по названию;
- отображение ближайших рейсов;
- сохранение избранных расписаний;
- работа в offline режиме.

Будьте бдительны:
- расписание составлено на основе общедоступных данных и не всегда может быть точным;
- приложение ориентируется на время, установленное в мобильном телефоне.
